message:
HI FRIENDS. I have a message to deliver from our good friend Hailey from Hawaii (she used to be in Cru but alas she is now back in Hawaii, no longer a student at the U, and can't access this page): 

"Wanna spend next summer in Hawaii? Come join Pacific House of Mission & work with military youth (6th-12th grade) on multiple military bases on Oahu, HI. You'll spend your summer planning & leading weekly bible studies, coordinating sports nights and special events for the youth throughout the summer, and building relationships with the staff & youth. Feel free to send me an email @ hailey.shaul14@gmail.com even if you're slightly interested!! I'd be happy to answer any questions you might have :) 

http://www.pacifichouseofmission.com/internship-program/ "

10/10 think Hailey is an awesome human, so if even you aren't interested, email her anyway and say hi. ¯\_(ツ)_/¯
